author: ForrestKnight
description:
To try everything Brilliant has to offer for free for a full 30 days, visit http://brilliant.org/ForrestKnight/ and get 20% off Brilliant’s annual premium subscription.

I built the same CLI app in five system programming languages: C, C++, Rust, Go, and Zig. Not to crown a winner—just to explore the tradeoffs like performance vs safety, simplicity vs power, minimalism vs… generics. It was a fun one. Enjoy!
